* Use of select command to display a menu of names

PS3='select names : '
names='Anu priya supriya quit'
select name in $names
do
if [ $name == 'quit' ]
then
break
fi
echo hello $name
done

OUTPUT

1) Anu 
2) Priya
3) Supriya
4) quit
select names : 1
hello Anu
select names : 2
hello priya
select names : 3
hello supriya 
select names : 4
